data.description: DECEMBER SPECIAL!! Sellers are offering their home under market value!!! This 3b/1b RANCH offers two living areas, a 4th non conforming bedroom with an easily added 2nd bath in lower level. Exceptionally maintained, perfect price for first time home buyers or investors looking to grow their portfolio. Access to shopping, dining, highways and park within minutes. The sellers have loved this home and the neighborhood but have simply outgrown the space.
